{"tid":1585740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果各位有辦法喺黨鐵封站+犬隻恐嚇嘅情況下號召到過百萬人集中喺同一區域嘅話，我支持十一集中行動","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T09:22:31.000Z","uid":230239,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15f605982f266353be614852681bd00a7bdbe5b5","tid":1585740,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:07:26.000Z","msg":"現實係白色恐怖已經嚇走咗好多人，只要啲狗唔批不反對，幾乎冇可能再發動到百萬人級數嘅活動，仲未計啲狗會一早開波嚇走和理非<br />\n而且出得嚟嘅人都會諗定後路，黨鐵一嚟料/set roadblocks就會斷後路，好多人會因為咁樣而唔參加，好難做得返6&middot;9嗰種盛況，分區活動大家對後路嘅顧慮會細好多<br />\n有冇堅持要集中嘅手足嚟說服我"},{"pid":"df78a2c7e883bd09cb933e9911f20c034095c06e","tid":1585740,"uid":230239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"好多人對情況太樂觀，但現實好殘酷<br />\n8&middot;18之後啲活動人數已經冇得攞嚟打飛機<br />\n唔好再幻想咁易有二百萬人出嚟"},{"pid":"662e2f832fc2c81ecfc7c6f7da4ca44562222d6c","tid":1585740,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"就算係前線手足都要路走架大佬<br />\n要集中唔係問題，但麻煩解決咗走唔到呢個問題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfebd04b111efe80cdeaf12688b898e78eda1552","tid":1585740,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662e2f832fc2c81ecfc7c6f7da4ca44562222d6c","tid":1585740,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"就算係前線手足都要路走架大佬<br />\n要集中唔係問題，但麻煩解決咗走唔到呢個問題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"有人話百萬人做後盾唔使走<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7aaa25bfee332e87cf1bee0e7fe317ec07d617","tid":1585740,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfebd04b111efe80cdeaf12688b898e78eda1552","tid":1585740,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662e2f832fc2c81ecfc7c6f7da4ca44562222d6c","tid":1585740,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-2